NHbrTemple.Description:
Primary structure. Can receive gathered resources.

Enables:
- Minions
NHbrTemple.Name: Temple

NHbrMinion.Description: Basic worker unit. Can gather resources and warp in Hybrid structures. Can sacrifice itself to become a Spirit.**Can attack ground units**
NHbrMinion.Name: Minion

NHbrSpirit.Description: Fast Hybrid Scout unit. Gets cloaking after upgrade.
NHbrSpirit.Name: Spirit

NHbrHarvester.Description: Warped in over a Vespene Geyser to allow harvesting of vespene gas.
NHbrHarvester.Name: Harvester

NHbrIonicCrystal.Description:
Provides supply. Supply allows you to warp in more units. Can teleport nearby Hybrid buildings to the target Network location.

Network Power Source.**Moveable structure**
NHbrIonicCrystal.Name: Ionic Crystal

NHbrIonicCrystal@Moveable.Description:
Provides supply. Supply allows you to warp in more units. Can teleport nearby Hybrid buildings to the target Network location.

Network Power Source.**Moveable structure**
NHbrIonicCrystal@Moveable.Name: Ionic Crystal

NHbrConstruct@AntiAir.Description:
Powerful Anti-Air guardian that test the strength of those who seek the Halls of Revelation. Can be transformed to Anti-Ground construct.

Can attack air units.
Detector
NHbrConstruct@AntiAir.Name: Construct (Anti-Air)

NHbrConstruct@AntiGround.Description:
Powerful Anti-Ground guardian that test the strength of those who seek the Halls of Revelation. Can be transformed to Anti-Air construct.

Can attack ground units.
Detector
NHbrConstruct@AntiGround.Name: Construct (Anti-Ground)

NHbrVoidRift.Description:
Warps in Hybrid units.

Enables:
- Warriors
NHbrVoidRift.Name: Void Rift

NHbrWarrior.Description:
General-purpose early-game infantry.

Can attack ground and air units.
NHbrWarrior.Name: Warrior

NHbrFlayer.Description: Ferocious mid-game annihilator of light-units.**Can attack ground units**
NHbrFlayer.Name: Flayer

NHbrWarbringer.Description: Potent mid-game destroyer of armored units. Can use «Mace Strike» to provide long-range support.**Can attack ground units**
NHbrWarbringer.Name: Warbringer

NHbrSentinel.Description: Mid-game fast unit. Can use Jump ability.**Can attack ground units**
NHbrSentinel.Name: Sentinel

NHbrReaver.Description: Late-game monstrous creature. Has a devastating melee attack.**Can attack ground units**
NHbrReaver.Name: Reaver

NHbrDominator.Description: Late-game psionic monstrous creature. Has a devastating ranged attack.**Can attack air and ground units**
NHbrDominator.Name: Dominator

NHbrDreadnok.Description:
Strong support unit that can disable casters.

Can attack ground and air units.
NHbrDreadnok.Name: Dreadnok

NHbrSilent.Description: Ranged mid-game support strider.**Can attack ground and air units**
NHbrSilent.Name: Silent

NHbrScreamer.Description:
Support mid-game air unit. Can restore Network to friendly units. Can use «Desolation» to cloak allies.

Restores 1.10 energy per second.

Detector

Can attack ground and air units.
NHbrScreamer.Name: Screamer

NHbrPollinator.Description: Air unit. Posions its target from the void.**Can attack ground units**
NHbrPollinator.Name: Pollinator

NHbrNavigator.Description:
Mid-game flying transport. Can teleport to any Void Portal.

Network Power Source.
NHbrNavigator.Name: Navigator

NHbrHorror.Description:
Late-game assault-tanky air unit. Deals splash damage to enemy air units and slows down ground units.

Can attack ground and air units.
NHbrHorror.Name: Horror

NHbrNemesis.Description:
Flagship air unit. Can use two attack modes.

Can attack ground and air units.
NHbrNemesis.Name: Nemesis

NHbrStasisCell.Description:
Improve Void Rifts connected to Stasis Cell in Network, containes upgrades for Hybrid units.

Connected Network Allows:
- Flayers
- Warbringers
- Sentinels
NHbrStasisCell.Name: Stasis Cell

NHbrVespeneConcentrator.Description: Contains specific upgrades for Hybrids. Build nearby Harvesters to increase their vespene amount.
NHbrVespeneConcentrator.Name: Vespene Concentrator

NHbrProcessingCore.Description:
Improve Void Rifts connected to Stasis Cell in Network. Contains upgrades for Hybrid units.

Connected Network Allows:
- Reavers
- Dominators
NHbrProcessingCore.Name: Processing Core

NHbrCrystallicShrine.Description:
Contains weapon and armor upgrades for Hybrid units

Connected Network Allows:
- Horrors
NHbrCrystallicShrine.Name: Crystallic Shrine

NHbrEngine.Description:
Containes upgrades for Hybrid units.

Enables:
- Silents
- Dreadnoks
NHbrEngine.Name: Engine

NHbrVoidPortal.Description:
Contains upgrades for Hybrid units.

Enables:
- Screamers
- Pollinators
- Navigators
NHbrVoidPortal.Name: Void Portal

NHbrProcessor.Description:
Contains upgrades for Hybrid units.

Enables:
- Upgrade Reaver to Advanced Reaver
- Upgrade Dominator to Advanced Dominator
NHbrProcessor.Name: Processor

NHbrNemesisCatacomb.Description:
Contains upgrades for Hybrid units.

Enables:
- Nemesis
NHbrNemesisCatacomb.Name: Nemesis Catacomb
